    {
      "type": "action",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
      "name": "Absorb Wraith",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Mandraivus the Lost extends its hand toward another wraith creature within 100 feet. The target wraith dissolves and streaks toward Mandraivus the Lost in a straight line, dealing [[/r {6d10}[negative]]]{6d10 negative damage} to each creature along the line (@Check[type:fortitude|dc:34|basic:true]). Mandraivus the Lost absorbs the essence of the target wraith, becoming @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Quickened]{Quickened} and gaining a +10-foot status bonus to its fly Speed for a number of rounds equal to the level of the absorbed wraith. It can use its extra action only to Fly or Strike. An unwilling target can attempt a @Check[type:will|dc:34] save to resist being absorbed.</p>"
        },
